{"tid":2511812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"影／印度青年為罹新冠母找到氧氣瓶 卻被警察搶給VIP用","createTime":"2021-05-01T07:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T09:10:39.000Z","uid":15564,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"729acbbe520fc3f6b59623baad4c79375b1ac745","tid":2511812,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T07:47:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"small\">2021-05-01 14:56 聯合報 編譯周辰陽／即時報導</span><br />\n<br />\n印度新冠肺炎大爆發正以全世界最快速度惡化，醫療器材嚴重短缺，公衛系統被壓垮，此時竟還發生警察被控強搶氧氣瓶給一位「VIP」使用，導致一位病危的女性新冠確診患者2小時後不幸身亡。<br />\n<br />\n印度時報特派記者拉維尼亞（Deepak Lavania）4月28日在推特分享影片，稱此事發生在北方邦亞格拉（Agra, Uttar Pradesh）一間私立醫院外，一名哭泣的男子向警察跪拜磕頭，狂求他們不要拿走他為病危母親找來的氧氣瓶，但很快被一名同樣穿著防護衣的人拉開，兩名工作人員則把氧氣瓶抬走。<br />\n<br />\n根據每日郵報與拉維尼亞4月30日在印度時報發布的報導指出，這名男子是17歲的安許（Ansh Goyal）。當醫院的氧氣用完後，安許與22歲的哥哥安默（Anmol Goyal）想辦法自行找到氧氣瓶，並且放到母親的病床旁。<br />\n<br />\n安默說，他試圖阻止氧氣瓶被拿走，卻被病房人員告知「VIP有需要」。這讓安許直跳腳，問警察稱「我要去哪裡找氧氣瓶，我來（到醫院）之前跟家人承諾，我會把媽媽活著帶回家」。<br />\n<br />\n安許接著表示，「我媽媽無法呼吸，我們為她做好幾次CPR，但救不了她。警察拿走氧氣瓶的2小時後，她就死了」。<br />\n<br />\n報導指當地警察本來否認指控，稱那一個氧氣瓶是空的，一位警司稱「男子要求警察提供他一個治療親屬的氧氣瓶，沒人拿走任何氧氣瓶，影片誤導」，卻沒有解釋警察為何被拍到拿走空氧氣瓶，亞格拉的副警察首長已下令展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dklavaniatoi/status/1387385303866888197?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdklavaniatoi%2Fstatus%2F1387385303866888197%3Fs%3D21&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRK7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=d916a68f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdklavaniatoi%2Fstatus%2F1387385303866888197%3Fs%3D21&h=3b4a0c29\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dklavaniatoi/status/1387385303866888197?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/05/01/realtime/12207186.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw-udn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F05%2F01%2Frealtime%2F12207186.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=239cc938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">印度時報特派記者拉維尼亞4月28日在推特分享影片，稱北方邦亞格拉一間私立醫院外前...</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/120944/5426751\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F120944%2F5426751&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRK7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=1579bbcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/120944/5426751</a>"},{"pid":"9dfba047797b86642d24bc7510a9e3d4e4d01951","tid":2511812,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T07:51:09.000Z","msg":"罹新冠母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c820c8373eb4b8080108ddfeef9e851596876c","tid":2511812,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T07:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8cc06aa4426cfa2f959be2c1b3b89a636a914c","tid":2511812,"uid":378793,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T07:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />竟然會救老母唔係強姦老母"},{"pid":"df971ea68e6ab93f0cf5fe7a1780921f87f96a41","tid":2511812,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d8cc06aa4426cfa2f959be2c1b3b89a636a914c","tid":2511812,"uid":378793,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T07:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />竟然會救老母唔係強姦老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T07:58:37.000Z","msg":"怕染疫反被騙！印度色狼誘「幫妳打疫苗」　少女慘遭綁手塞口性侵<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210501/1972026.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20210501%2F1972026.htm&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRK7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=43c65a2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20210501/1972026.htm</a>